extends layout

block content
    h1= title 
    p Welcome to #[em Bookshelf], a very basic Express website developed as a tutorial example on the Mozilla Developer Network.

    h1 Dynamic content 

    if err 
        p Error getting dynamic content 
    else 
        p The library has the following record counts:

        ul 
            li #[strong Books:] !{results.book_count}
            li #[strong Copies:] !{results.book_instance_count}
            li #[strong Copies available:] !{results.book_instance_available_count}
            li #[strong Authors:] !{results.author_count}
            li #[strong Genres:] !{results.genre_count}